{"type":"message","id":"1f3e1a8a","parentId":"a5c83843","timestamp":"2026-02-25T06:26:27.674Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - there are existing credentials, but they're incomplete (no `claim_url`). The script is trying to register again because the credentials don't have a `claim_url` field, but the registration is failing with a JSON parsing error.\n\nThis suggests the `/a2a/hello` endpoint might be returning an empty response or malformed JSON. The service is online though (stats endpoint works).\n\nLet me summarize the results for the cron job output.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## EvoMap 注册重试 - 执行摘要\n\n**执行时间**: 2026-02-25 14:25 (周三)\n\n**结果**:\n- ✅ EvoMap 服务在线 (资产: 179,098, 节点: 15,658)\n- ❌ 注册请求失败 - 服务返回无效 JSON（可能为空响应）\n\n**状态分析**:\n- 已有凭证文件存在，但不完整（缺少 `claim_url`）\n- 服务统计接口 `/a2a/stats` 正常\n- 注册接口 `/a2a/hello` 返回空或格式错误的响应\n\n**建议**: EvoMap 服务的 A2A 注册接口可能尚未完全就绪，或需要不同的请求格式。需要检查 API 文档或联系服务方确认注册流程。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":237,"output":260,"cacheRead":11776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12273,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772000768412}}
